314829937.Title: matrix decor 2.1 cu. ft. Upright Freezer with Reversible Adjustable Door in Stainless Steel, Black
314829937.Description: This is a mini Upright Freezer Measuring at 17.5*22*25.4, this freezer with its flush back design fits in the smallest of spaces, while still delivering 2.1 cu. ft. of storage area. It is also designed to save you energy. Reverse the door as you prefer, and store all your go-to foods on 2 accessible shelves. It will be a welcome addition to your home and keeping you ready with food supplies for your family. Color: Black.

314829183.Title: matrix decor 1.1 cu. ft. Upright Freezer with Reversible Adjustable Door in Stainless Steel, Black
314829183.Description: The 1.1 cu. ft. upright freezer gives you the extra frozen food storage space you're looking for. It is perfect for smaller spaces, especially in apartments, office break rooms, vacation condos and mobile homes. The reversible door and flush-back design offers placement flexibility for any compact space. Color: Black.

302174741.Title: Summit Appliance 2.7 cu. ft. Frost Free Upright Freezer with Panel-Ready Door in Black, Panel-Ready/ Black
302174741.Description: SUMMIT brings true convenience to small kitchen spaces with the SCFF1842IFADA, an 18 in. wide fully frost-free all-freezer designed for use under lower ADA compliant counters.The 32 in. high SCFF1842IFADA is front-breathing for built-in use under counters, but also features a fully finished jet black cabinet to allow freestanding use. The door includes an integrated stainless steel frame designed to accept full overlay panels for a custom look (panel size: 17-1/2 in. W x 27-3/4 in. H; maximum weight: 10 lbs.). Users provide their own handle.Inside, the SCFF1842IFADA is fully frost-free to minimize user maintenance, with slide-out chrome shelves that can be adjusted to accommodate a variety of items in the 2.7 cu. ft. interior. This unit includes a digital thermostat for easy and intuitive temperature control.With a uniquely slim size and user-friendly features, the SCFF1842IFADA is the ideal freezer for space-challenged spaces. This model meets UL-471 standards. Color: Panel-Ready/ Black.

303842128.Title: Gladiator 17.8 cu. ft. Upright Rolling Garage Freezer in Black
303842128.Description: The Industrys Only Step-to-Open Upright Freezer makes it easy to stock up when your arms are full. And even in extreme temperatures from 0°F to 110°F, our garage freezer keeps it all properly frozen. The hammered granite cabinet and black matte door finish create the perfect look for the garage.

314009951.Title: Commercial Cool 2.8 cu. ft. Upright Freezer White
314009951.Description: Where space is at a premium, this compact, 2.8 cu. ft. upright freezer is the perfect solution. Despite a small footprint, there is still plenty of room when you've maxed out the freezer portion of your fridge and still want to stock up on sales items or ready for that big party. The Commercial Cool 2. 8 cu. ft. Upright freezer features a reversible door, adjustable thermostat, adjustable leveling legs and 3 Full-width interior shelves. Color: White.

302175051.Title: Summit Appliance 4.7 cu. ft. Frost Free Upright Freezer With Panel-Ready Door In Black, Panel-Ready/ Black
302175051.Description: SUMMIT's SCFF53B Series brings quality and convenience under the counter with a fully featured lineup of built-in frost-free all-freezers.Sized with a convenient 24 in. footprint, the SCFF53BIF freezer can be used built-in or freestanding. It has a black cabinet with a sealed back for easy cleaning. The door features an integrated stainless steel frame designed to accept full overlay panels, letting you seamlessly blend the unit into your own cabinetry design. Users provide their own handle to complete the custom look.Inside, the SCFF53BIF utilizes frost-free operation with fan-forced cooling to ensure low maintenance and even temperature distribution. Recessed LED lighting offers an attractive yet efficient look. The digital thermostat makes it easy to manage the interior temperature. This unit includes adjustable chrome shelves for flexible storage. Additional features include an open door alarm, high temperature alarm and Sabbath mode setting that lets you disable some of the electrical elements during periods of observance.The SCFF53BIF freezer is ETL-S listed to NSF-7 commercial standards. With its deluxe style and user-friendly features, this unit is the perfect choice for home or commercial kitchens. Color: Panel-Ready/ Black.
